data.name: txtCSNeedHeating.ToolTip
data.value:
Cloud sensor needs heating flag.
This is only narrow condition test - if cloud index in given interval and steadily decreasign during last 5 5min cylcles (exact settings are set in Preferences in "CS auto heating settings" group)
But for heating switching on also another conditions must be met: - since last relay switching on passed at least ... minutes (set in "CS auto heating settings") - humidity is 100% - there is no rain now - it is dark now
